{"title":"中国民歌","authors":["李世恩"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":9,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李世恩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从在河之洲的雎鸠关关声里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从日出东南隅的阡陌桑田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我认识了民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它原本是一种无状的植物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的根须"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深扎在《诗经》的最深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如一枝立在水中央的萋萋蒹葭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年风雨不衰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还可以把它想象成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种青铜之辉，抑或"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种古陶之韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琤琤琮琮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘满理性的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神秘且难以触摸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实，民歌的蕴涵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不仅限于此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是一枚民族文化的标本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夹在线装的历史书里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让一代一代人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咀嚼"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}